{"type": "article", "id": 19916, "title": "看完这堆照片，2015 年设计界什么值得留念就都在这儿了", "description": "wallpaper 网站的年终盘点", "date": "2015-12-30T19:08:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6296, "name": "年度盘点"}, {"id": 5340, "name": "2015"}, {"id": 21289, "name": "设计回顾"}, {"id": 21290, "name": "设计图片"}, {"id": 5281, "name": "Wallpaper"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 279, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114204lpiMjcr9q7B6NFRS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t转眼 2015 年只剩下最后两天了。过去的一年里，世界各地的设计师们创造了许多惊艳的作品，让世界又美好了那么一点点。近日，<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/gallery/design/2015-in-review-the-year-in-pictures#140488\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper 网站通过 50 张图片回顾了设计界的一整年</a>，堪称视觉大餐。我们选取了一些，并配以简单的图注。希望明年设计界能更加精彩纷呈。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114146VxS9DFPRG6b84IHq.gif\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61298701\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114147rUT9eWZMqIRbjLih.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">上图中的织物和家具是由 Raf Simons 和 Kvadrat 设计的，它们获得了 Wallpaper* Design Awards 2015\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114148jZT7goxhBeHurGFO.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">上图中的建筑位于瑞士，名叫 InterContinental Davos，它是丛林中一处不（ang）错（gui）的隐居之所\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114149vo384TRlDCwJrmN9.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t纽约建筑事务所 <span>Steven Holl </span>设计的台湾金宝山公墓，上图为概念图\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114149vYdBJfG2L9CycbXt.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><em>Chanel Couture S/S 2015 大秀</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114150ZitlIjP058FnQSxq.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">Ghost Chair ，设计者是 Ingrid 和 Olle Wingård \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114150omxyYP5kWi4Cbt86.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">上图中是名为“地心引力”的男装秀场，这是品牌 <span style=\"text-align:center;\">Phillip Lim 的秀场</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114150ZxBt98vb6fawGDU2.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">这是一个位于挪威的教堂，名叫 Knarvik Community Church,设计者是 Reiulf Ramstad Arkitekter\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071141513Ic1HhZr4PQzspd5.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">马德里设计事务所 SelgasCano 所设计的步行道\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060711415131dLz6wcjM5QIBOf.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这个装置位于法国城市 <span>Saint-Étienne</span>，叫作 <span>Form Follows Information</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114152LCTSJGhr153I7ukn.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> <span style=\"text-align:center;\">Morgan Aero 8，它亮相于 </span>2015 Geneva Motor Show </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114153XTzb1dftgKY4uZLw.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Tom Dixon 设计的灯</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114153CqPtbErx04L7UDM2.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t时装品牌<span> COS </span>和纽约建筑事务所 <span>Snarkitecture </span>合作设计的装置\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114154ISzVhtb36md8Ka42.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">Hyères International Festival 上的摄影作品\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071141542AwfUR5yjHPqLT6a.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">2015 米兰世博会上的建筑，设计者是 Nemesi &amp; Partners.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114155tpAU3JIxrHTCEhMn.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">2015 威尼斯双年展上的装置，名叫 “I Scream Daddio”\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071141556lS2XusQmngOCdAG.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这是位于芬兰的 <span>Dream Hotel</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071141563aW7zkrVSCdntNHf.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">这是位于瑞士的小屋，名叫 House in Rombach\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114156Xhcnmu1jIJEAyrKi.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.68526316\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Wallpaper* Motel</span>，室内设计采用了中世纪的古旧风格\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114157L5FSksam9iZOg46y.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t位于迈阿密的 <span>One Thousand Museum, </span>设计者是<span> Zaha Hadid</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071141578euD7A6zPp095gdv.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">丹麦新品牌 Reform 设计的餐桌\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114158uVA65cmPdkKDvZhy.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t在今夏的摩纳哥，出现了一个潘通<span> pop-up </span>咖啡厅\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114158sZ0zKLC39npM8vjJ.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t英国伦敦的“桃树屋”，设计方是 <span>Edgley Design</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114159thcZLyMBFjHkX4uS.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/london-design-festival/2015\">London Design\r\nFestival 2015</a></span>，挪威展厅一角\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114200jy7CsPOLUd2cXnxH.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">上图是洛杉矶新的现代艺术博物馆\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114200jtIK7zbUA1qhpmF3.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t纽约 <span>Anthea Hamilton </span>展\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114201u6HxXkDFC2bK5eqA.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Laith McGregor </span>和<span> Murray\r\nBarker </span>设计的乒乓球台\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114201xN7GKbWJ53cgOauj.gif\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Apple Pencil</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114202403zJnhKXVDxlNFk.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t迪奥秀场  Delphinium-hill\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114202Y1imWIUb6loOdB73.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这架飞机来自私人航空公司<span> Netjets，它首次亮相于 Design Miami 2015</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114203ARxWq7GkUpaDE6F0.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t位于纽约的 <span>Sun Path House</span>，它由纽约设计师 <span>Christian Wassman </span>设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114204danxib7TAwmV5W0I.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t位于哥本哈根的 <span>The Blue Planet </span>，设计者是 <span>3XN</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/gallery/design/2015-in-review-the-year-in-pictures#138849\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}